snippet.title: What are Actions on Google (Assistant on Air)
snippet.description:
In the first episode of Assistant on Air, Luke Davis and guest Jessica Dene Early-Cha introduce the concept of Actions on Google, and talk about common terminology.

Actions on Google docs → http://bit.ly/2YabdS5

Other episodes of Assistant on Air → https://goo.gle/2X0nBqG
Subscribe to Google Devs for the latest Actions on Google videos →  https://bit.ly/googledevs
